divs: sighting detailsawoke at 4:30, 30 minutes before my alarm clock was to go off to get up, and left my dogs out as i do every morning. decided to get into the hot tub, and noticed 4 lights in a square or diamond shape. it was right before sunrise, approximate altitude was 1 mile above. object traveled in a straight line traveling in west direction from york towards gettysburg. object disappeared into some clouds. there was no sound what so ever. * this light was blinking white then orange\yellow * *this light was blinking white then orange\yellow *these two lights were steady orange\yellow lights
